3405
05:18:12,868 --> 05:18:14,389
That's the best in the commonwealth.

3406
05:18:14,590 --> 05:18:16,151
Almost the best in the commonwealth.

3407
05:18:16,371 --> 05:18:17,192
You should be proud of that.

3408
05:18:17,252 --> 05:18:18,273
You support the schools.

3409
05:18:18,573 --> 05:18:20,195
The school committee supports the schools.

3410
05:18:20,215 --> 05:18:21,836
You should be proud of that.

3411
05:18:22,477 --> 05:18:23,758
Because you've got good class size.

3412
05:18:23,778 --> 05:18:29,764
Because you've asked the question about class size over and over again at the various meetings that I've attended on budget.

3413
05:18:30,504 --> 05:18:32,766
So I think you should have that as you go into the campaign.

3414
05:18:33,107 --> 05:18:33,988
I think you should know that.

3415
05:18:34,870 --> 05:18:41,278
