3427
05:19:38,930 --> 05:19:41,971
Now there may be some need for some looking at distribution.

3428
05:19:42,672 --> 05:19:44,693
One school maybe has a little bit less than another.

3429
05:19:45,273 --> 05:19:46,473
That's always the case.

3430
05:19:46,513 --> 05:19:47,234
You work on that.

3431
05:19:48,214 --> 05:20:02,280
